        "readme": {
          "childMarkdownRemark": {
            "html": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://themes.lekoarts.de\">\n    <img alt=\"Gatsby Theme\" src=\"https://img.lekoarts.de/gatsby/gatsby-themes-illustration.png\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n<h1 align=\"center\">\n  @lekoarts/gatsby-theme-status-dashboard\n</h1>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/LekoArts/gatsby-themes/blob/master/LICENSE\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg\" alt=\"@lekoarts/gatsby-theme-status-dashboard is released under the MIT license.\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.org/package/@lekoarts/gatsby-theme-status-dashboard\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/v/@lekoarts/gatsby-theme-status-dashboard.svg\" alt=\"Current npm package version.\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://npmcharts.com/compare/@lekoarts/gatsby-theme-status-dashboard?minimal=true\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/dm/@lekoarts/gatsby-theme-status-dashboard.svg\" alt=\"Downloads per month on npm.\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://npmcharts.com/compare/@lekoarts/gatsby-theme-status-dashboard?minimal=true\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/dt/@lekoarts/gatsby-theme-status-dashboard.svg\" alt=\"Total downloads on npm.\">\n  </a>\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/PRs-welcome-brightgreen.svg\" alt=\"PRs welcome!\">\n  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/follow?screen_name=lekoarts_de\">\n      <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/twitter/follow/lekoarts_de.svg?label=Follow%20@lekoarts_de\" alt=\"Follow @lekoarts_de\">\n    </a>\n</p>\n<p>Show the live statuses of your Netlify and CircleCI builds on your website! Easily integrate the customizable components into your site and adapt them to your theme (utilizing Theme UI).</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://status.lekoarts.de\"><strong>Demo Website</strong></a> (<a href=\"https://github.com/LekoArts/gatsby-status-dashboard\">Source Code</a>)</p>\n<p>Also be sure to checkout other <a href=\"https://themes.lekoarts.de\">Free &#x26; Open Source Gatsby Themes</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"features\"><a href=\"#features\" aria-label=\"features permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Use the theme’s components <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Info /&gt;</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Grid /&gt;</code> to display:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The number of Netlify sites and CircleCI projects you have</li>\n<li>All public Netlify sites you have in a grid including statuses of CircleCI if configured in the repository</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Theme UI-based theming</li>\n<li>Uses the status badges meaning the statuses are live and don’t need a re-build</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"installation\"><a href=\"#installation\" aria-label=\"installation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installation</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">npm install @lekoarts/gatsby-theme-status-dashboard</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"install-as-a-starter\"><a href=\"#install-as-a-starter\" aria-label=\"install as a starter permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install as a starter</h3>\n<p>This will generate a new site that pre-configures use of the theme. Perfect for a single-page usage (e.g. <code class=\"language-text\">https://status.your-domain.tld</code>).</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">gatsby new status-dashboard LekoArts/gatsby-status-dashboard</code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/LekoArts/gatsby-status-dashboard\"><strong>View the starter’s code</strong></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-label=\"usage permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<h3 id=\"theme-options\"><a href=\"#theme-options\" aria-label=\"theme options permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Theme options</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Key</th>\n<th>Default Value</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">netlifyOptions</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">{}</code></td>\n<td>Pass options to <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-source-netlify</code> (<a href=\"https://github.com/LekoArts/gatsby-source-netlify#options\">Read the plugin’s documentation</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 id=\"example-usage\"><a href=\"#example-usage\" aria-label=\"example usage permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Example usage</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">@lekoarts/gatsby-theme-status-dashboard</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// netlifyOptions defaults to `{}`</span>\n        netlifyOptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          userAgent<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">netlify/js-client</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"environment-variables\"><a href=\"#environment-variables\" aria-label=\"environment variables permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Environment variables</h3>\n<p>You <strong>must</strong> have two environment variables configured in your project as the theme relies on them: <code class=\"language-text\">NETLIFY_ACCESS_KEY</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">CIRCLECI_KEY</code>. Otherwise the theme can’t access information from the source plugins.</p>\n<p>You can read <a href=\"https://github.com/LekoArts/gatsby-source-netlify#prerequisites\"><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-source-netlify</code>’s documentation</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/LekoArts/gatsby-source-circleci#prerequisites\"><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-source-circleci</code>’s documentation</a> to learn how to obtain your API keys.</p>\n<p>Gatsby also has <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/docs/environment-variables/\">official documentation</a> on environment variables.</p>\n<p>Lastly you should have a look at the <a href=\"https://github.com/LekoArts/gatsby-themes/tree/master/examples/status-dashboard\">example site</a> if you need further help.</p>\n<h3 id=\"components\"><a href=\"#components\" aria-label=\"components permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Components</h3>\n<p>This theme doesn’t setup an individual page but rather exposes two React components:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Info</code>: Displays the number of Netlify websites and CircleCI projects (e.g. “18 Websites” and “7 CircleCI Projects”)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Grid</code>: Displays the sites in a card grid (using CSS Grid). The individual cards contain the name of the site, links to GitHub and CircleCI, and displays the Netlify deploy status &#x26; optionally the CircleCI status</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"usage-1\"><a href=\"#usage-1\" aria-label=\"usage 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h4>\n<p>Import the components into your file and use them like normal React components (see <a href=\"https://github.com/LekoArts/gatsby-themes/tree/master/examples/status-dashboard/src/pages/index.jsx\">example</a>):</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Info <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@lekoarts/gatsby-theme-status-dashboard\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Index</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Info</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Grid</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Index<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"formatters\"><a href=\"#formatters\" aria-label=\"formatters permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Formatters</h3>\n<p>The Netlify API doesn’t update the paths to GitHub when you e.g. change your username (it’ll keep the one from the time you created the Netlify project). As the theme will use the GitHub URLs from Netlify projects to check against CircleCI (to see if it can find CircleCI projects with the same GitHub URL), they need to be the same.</p>\n<p>Hence this theme allows to shadow a <code class=\"language-text\">formatters</code> file. It’ll be used to replace words in the URL, e.g. replace <code class=\"language-text\">LeKoArts</code> with <code class=\"language-text\">LekoArts</code>. You can find the file in <code class=\"language-text\">src/utils</code>.</p>",
